## 8. Medusa V1 Extension Patterns (How to Add Custom Features)

### Custom API Routes
```
src/api/store/{feature}/route.ts     ← Public storefront endpoints
src/api/admin/{feature}/route.ts     ← Admin-only endpoints
```
- Express-style route handlers
- Access Medusa services via `req.scope.resolve("serviceName")`
- Auth middleware available for protected routes

### Custom Models (TypeORM Entities)
```ts
// src/models/my-entity.ts
import { BaseEntity } from "@medusajs/medusa"
import { Entity, Column } from "typeorm"

@Entity()
export class MyEntity extends BaseEntity {
  @Column()
  name: string
}
```

