## 11. Redis Keys Structure (for Rate Limiting + OTP)

```
# OTP storage
otp:{mobile}              → hashed OTP value, TTL 300s
otp:attempts:{mobile}     → attempt count, TTL 600s
otp:send_count:{mobile}   → send count (rate limit), TTL 600s

# Rate limiting
ratelimit:gen:{customer_id}    → last generation timestamp, TTL 30s
ratelimit:gen:daily:{customer_id} → daily count, TTL 86400s
ratelimit:ip:{ip}              → request count, TTL 60s

# Generation lock
genlock:{customer_id}          → "1" while generation in-flight, TTL 120s
```

